Package: cardiometR
Title: Cardiopulmonary Exercise Testing Analysis with S7 Classes
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Jonathan", "Tremblay", email = "jonathan.tremblay@umontreal.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Import, process, and report cardiopulmonary exercise testing (CPET)
    data from COSMED Quark CPET metabolic carts. Uses S7 classes for type-safe
    data structures. Includes a Shiny application for interactive analysis and
    bilingual (English/French) PDF report generation via Typst.
